---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Contact Us - Asianfoodsdaily"
  description="Get in touch with Asian Foods Daily for recipe questions, feedback, or collaboration inquiries."

  ogType="website"
  noIndex={false}>
  <main class="py-24 bg-white" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:5wycxj">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1i">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1j">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-zinc-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:xwwf0o">Contact Us</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga1d">We'd love to hear from you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1k">
        <div data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1l">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:j8hht3">Get In Touch</h2>
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1m">
            <p class="text-zinc-600 mb-2" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga1e">Email:</p>
            <a href="mailto:hello@asianfoodsdaily.com" class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:piidcf">
              hello@asianfoodsdaily.com
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed italic" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga1f">
            We typically respond within 24-48 hours. Sometimes sooner if we're already at our computers obsessing over recipe details.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1n">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:j8hht2">What You Can Reach Out About</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1o">
            <div data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1p">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:4k2kkv">Recipe questions</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga21">Stuck on a technique? Need a substitution? Want clarification on an ingredient? Ask away.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1q">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:4k2kku">Your results</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga22">Made one of our recipes? We genuinely want to know how it turned out. Photos welcome.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:lx8n1r">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:4k2kkt">Recipe requests</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga23">Looking for a specific dish? We keep a list and work through it.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:uoopef">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:4k2kks">Corrections</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga24">Spotted an error or something unclear? Please tell us so we can fix it.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:uoopee">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:4k2kkr">Collaborations</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga25">Have an idea for working together? Send us the details.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:uooped">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:4k2kkq">General feedback</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga26">Thoughts on the site, suggestions for improvement, or just want to talk about food? We're listening.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-24 pt-16 border-t border-zinc-100" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:uoopec">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:j8hhsg">A Few Notes</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-zinc-600" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:uoopeb">
          <ul class="space-y-4 list-disc pl-5">
            <li data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:jzge9e">We read and respond to every email personally. No auto-replies, no canned responses.</li>
            <li data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:jzge9d">If you're asking about a specific recipe, including the recipe name or link helps us give you a better answer faster.</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="space-y-4 list-disc pl-5">
            <li data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:jzge9c">For time-sensitive questions (like "I'm cooking this tonight and..."), put that in your subject line. We'll prioritize it.</li>
            <li data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:jzge9b">We don't sell or share your email address. Ever.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 text-center bg-zinc-900 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:uoopea">
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga27">Direct Email</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@asianfoodsdaily.com" class="text-3xl font-bold hover:text-red-500 transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:piidcg">
            hello@asianfoodsdaily.com
          </a>
          <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-500 italic" data-ps="src/pages/contact.astro:wmga28">That's it. Just email us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
